Hi Everyone. Is it possible to create a HubL script that sorts data from a custom object AND a HubDB table? I am trying with the code below but I cant get it to work.
```{% set invoice_number = order_fulfillment.invoice_number %}
{% set query = "eq" ~ invoice_number %}
{% set order_fulfillment = hubdb_table_rows(table_id=16113438, query=query) %}

{% for row in order_fulfillment %}
    &lt;a href="{{ row.invoice_url }}"&gt;
        &lt;img src="<https://6257192.fs1.HubSpotusercontent-na1.net/hubfs/6257192/PAY-NOW-Button.png>" alt="PAY NOW" style="outline: none; max-width: 100%;" width="260px"&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;
{% endfor %}```
